fulltitle: Bobby Watson Interview by Dr. Michael Woods - 1/19/1996 - Clinton, NY
title: Bobby Watson Interview by Dr. Michael Woods - 1/19/1996 - Clinton, NY
description:
Saxophonist Bobby Watson talks about the influences on his sound, ranging from experiences in the black church to his time with Art Blakey.
